        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Based on the reactions it looks like there is no support for doing this, at least currently. But then I'm wondering what are we waiting for? What potential changes to the \"final holistic state\" could there be that would make this premature? \r\n\r\nI thought we are already on a clear path to our options handling, and I don't see any potential for a more ideal function signature (i.e. extra parameters or changed return-value structure).",
