            "body": "> I thought we are already on a clear path to our options handling, and I don't see any potential for a more ideal function signature (i.e. extra parameters or changed return-value structure).\r\n\r\nClear goal, but the road is twisty. Don't expect the expected; expect the unexpected. I am worried that we'll hit a roadblock somewhere that will force us to change tack, or that the needed changes will have unforeseen performance impacts that will invalidate your current analysis.",
